Interface WorldManager


  • public interface WorldManager
    This is a container for all of the worlds.

    Jos Kuijpers, Jason (darkdiplomat)

      • unloadWorld

        void unloadWorld(java.lang.String name,
                 DimensionType type,
                 boolean force)
        Unloads a world, effectively removing it from the servers tick loop, until it is loaded again.
        The world will be saved before it is unloaded. It is NOT unloaded if there are still players tracked in it.
        Parameters:
        name - The base name
        type - The dimension type
        force - Will kick players in this world before unloading, making it possible to unload the world.
